多過十句唔會覺得有分別。"},{"pid":"d30d5a52b9e8d0a3d30e45dd663373fccadcfe8f","tid":126526,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到口臭啦！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再將台灣國語講成「國語」啦</span><br />\n<br />\n叫得國語，就係自己國家用嘅正式語言。你係咪當台灣係你嘅祖國？<br />\nNo! <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地嘅國語就係廣東話/粵語。</span></span><br />\n正如一個英國人嘅國語就係英語咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n所以係時候改下口啦，由小改變大中華灌輸嘅習慣，應該好簡單姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npish"},{"pid":"57ea9c27e65dab5501b818def803dccd866da554","tid":126526,"uid":78700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我試過咁對人<br />\n個男遊客問我路,見佢講普通話本來想敷衍佢<br />\n點知佢話自己係台灣人,我自己得閒就帶埋佢去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagree，對台灣人就可以好d<br />\n之前試過見支那人問路，老點左佢去反方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSAME <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f217db7e2c7967b8e012f5329a1918a97f7cd1","tid":126526,"uid":17211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港客，自己人，正常料or或者畀靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陸客，豪爽的話，雖然叫嘅一樣，但會畀好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台客，會加料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解台客要加料?</blockquote><br />\n又西又孤寒又無見識，重要不斷表現到同大6人唔同(大聲講台語，乜柒都怎麼這樣，我都沒看過，好厲害啊)，但又唔知好影響其他人，又唔知顯得自己自卑"},{"pid":"ab7a2f795558f8f5b1d12954b35820855b54b13